46
00:05:58,700 --> 00:06:01,460
His hand suddenly trembled at a crucial time.

47
00:06:01,460 --> 00:06:04,690
He said that his hand was hurt because he had been copying the scriptures to pray for blessings for His Majesty.

48
00:06:04,690 --> 00:06:06,840
