108
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:17,990
Without seeing the person, I really can't treat the patient.

109
00:10:17,990 --> 00:10:22,910
But Pei Xingjian kept begging and was very sincere,

110
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:26,170
