111
00:10:26,170 --> 00:10:29,870
A young lady? You didn't even see her.

112
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:32,360
How do you know it's a young lady?

113
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,300
You don't know this, but

114
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:37,900
