324
00:27:21,390 --> 00:27:24,480
Please give me the medicine, Your Highness.

325
00:27:55,650 --> 00:27:59,120
Buddha, eleven years ago,

326
00:27:59,120 --> 00:28:02,340
I altered Liuli's fortune stick in front of you.

327
