439
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:53,460
Here, please keep it well.

440
00:37:54,210 --> 00:37:56,110
I remember.

441
00:37:59,270 --> 00:38:01,780
Physician Heng, they call you Devine Hua Tuo.
