443
00:38:04,470 --> 00:38:07,990
Thank you.

444
00:38:07,990 --> 00:38:10,920
You're welcome.

445
00:38:11,850 --> 00:38:15,410
I will leave for now.

446
00:38:28,530 --> 00:38:32,770
